{"title":"2-11H. nocriz卡管道","time_limit":750,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2019小学期"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1116#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1116","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1116/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1116/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1116"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"在二维空间中，有一个宽度为$l$的二维管道，我们可以视其为一条$y=l$的直线与$x$轴所夹的部分，管道的长度为正无穷。\r\n\r\n这个管道中有个$n$个钉子，第$i$个钉子的坐标为$(x_i,y_i)$。\r\n\r\n已知有一个圆，能在不碰钉子不碰壁的前提下，从管道的最左端移动最右端。即从横坐标负无穷的地方走到横坐标正无穷的地方。\r\n\r\n求这个圆的直径最大是多少。为了避免精度误差，请输出答案保留三位小数的结果。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行两个整数$n,l$。\r\n\r\n接下来$n$行，每行两个整数$x_i,y_i$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行一个三位小数表示答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```\r\n1 5\r\n2 2\r\n```\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n3.000\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\le n \\le 500 $\r\n\r\n$1 \\le y_i < l \\le 10000$\r\n\r\n$-10000 \\le x_i \\le 10000$。\r\n"}]}